            "term": "Ajal",
            "definition": "Masa berakhir"
        },
        {
            "type": "definition",
            "term": "Wafat",
            "definition": "Sempurna"
        },
        {
            "type": "definition",
            "term": "Maut",
            "definition": "Dicabut (ruh)"
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Urutan: Wafat, Ajal, dan Maut. Wadi'ah adalah titipan dari Allah SWT."
        },
